window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Succubus is beautiful, deadly, and prowling the night for victims as their leader creates a plan to take New York City for her own dark purposes.</p> <p>But Kurt is there, and by freeing Succubi from their ancient curse, he will build a team of elite killers who will stalk the night with revenge on their minds.</p> <p>Join the hunter as he tames succubi, magic, and a weapon as old as time in his search of destiny.</p>"; 
